{"tid":1996304,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［警世］今次天馬個「造勢」模式同上年紅媒屈911有「焦土行動」好似","createTime":"2020-05-01T01:15:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-01T01:53:15.000Z","uid":48124,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"2ad5d334dcc3e320bfd3421971d1803339d6c06c","tid":1996304,"uid":48124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T01:15:39.000Z","msg":"同樣係自己人咩都冇聽過，但紅媒就一早放晒風上晒頭版<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aWGercG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaWGercG.png&h=9c7aa485&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n同樣係將所有行動放到最極端，好方便官方推落去佢哋最常用嘅用字：「恐怖主義」<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v2rVaEP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv2rVaEP.jpg&h=874ac683&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n活動喺藍絲圈子廣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但係手足之間就非常具爭議性（上次係覺得911 有行動令美國反感不符合connect精神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）（同埋所謂無差別攻擊/炸油管..本身就好具爭議性/完全唔係同路人會諗出嚟嘅嘢）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Pd0KOr5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPd0KOr5.jpg&h=21768d45&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n嚴重懷疑呢兩次活動其實都係同一班人諗出嚟（可能唔單止班狗、仲要係極接近官方嘅人士）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n方便佢哋推行所謂嘅國安法/23條<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n上次對家唔成功，係因為一大班手足極力反對極力勸喻大家唔好出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今次根本就係同一條橋打算再做多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家睇路"},{"pid":"7c489d52f161ec2b51681f53e72f8b46d767172f","tid":1996304,"uid":172303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T01:17:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ee132c335727147023b65a4deb888d90ff5e5cc0","tid":1996304,"uid":214502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-0